Name: Your Wrestling Entrance Music (redux)
Description: Sam's rules: I want to hear ring names, personas, finishing moves etc in the comments

Name: Best vibe fit music video
Description: Submit a YouTube link with your song. The best visual vibe fit for the song. No obvious choices.

Name: "How did I not know this song existed?"
Description: a song by a fairly well-known band that is weird, or out-of-character, or a surprising collab etc, but which isn't well known (extra votes if you haven't heard it)

Name: songs about animals
Description:
not animal body parts, just songs bout animals

Name: You probably haven’t heard this cover
Description: Cover songs by bands that have less than 50k monthly listeners

Name: guest submission redux
Description: Hand your phone to a partner/family member/friend. Tell us about them in the comments.

Name: A song that is the equivalent of a Saturday morning bowl of cereal
Description: A song that evokes the feeling of waking up on a Saturday with no work, pouring yourself a bowl of cereal, and just vibing with the morning. Tell us what cereal you're having.

Name: Song with a surprise
Description: This one is a little more open to interpretation than other rounds. For comments, you might want to provide a timestamp or hint at the type of surprise. Definitely don't walk us through the surprise in detail.

Name: A Song That Just Came Out That Isn’t Taylor Swift
Description: Submit a song released in the last few weeks... that isn't T Swift.

Name: "You Wouldn't Have Heard of Them" Classic
Description: Choose a great song that you think we won't have heard (voting rule - if you've heard the band before then you can't give it any votes. If you've only heard OF the band... you can vote.)
